Orange Is The New Orange
Episode 8 — March 6, 2018 — Ben See-Tho, Lucas Watkins

"There are a lot of things that I imagined for myself. Like as a freshman I was like, when Im a senior Im gonna be on one of those red squares. Im gonna be lying down during G period in the sun. But now there are no red squares. You wish they were orange squares though, lets be real.
